@startuml
' @id(CMP-ARCH-CLI)
' @desc(CMP-ARCH-CLI, "Implemented as the mdd-cli `mdd arch` nested subcommand (Commands::Arch -> ArchCommand::Diff/Status, --json) plus the mdd-core architecture.rs engine (ArchitectureSpec parse, pure diff(), pure check(), and Project::read_text_at_ref git-show base reader). Distinct from CMP-ARCH-TRACKING (the spec artifact + templates + agent doc): this is the tooling that diffs and gates it; check() is also called by Project::validate_inner.")
' Current-side component for the architecture CLI + engine (cycle 0029).
title Architecture CLI + engine (current)

component "mdd arch (CLI)\nmdd-cli Commands::Arch" as Cli
component "architecture.rs engine\n(parse / diff / check)" as Engine
component "mdd validate\n(Project::validate_inner)" as Validate
artifact ".mdd/architecture/*.yml" as Spec
component "git" as Git

Cli --> Engine : diff / status
Engine --> Spec : parse working
Engine --> Git : read base at ref (git show)
Validate --> Engine : check() as WARNING rules
@enduml
